# COMPILER/BOOT/iii_cycle_family.def
#
# SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for the nine KATABASIS descent cycle families
# (DOCS/III-KATABASIS.md plan 3.0).  CHARIOT's ~90 IOCTLs collapse into nine
# hexad-distinguished families; this table is their taxonomy -- each family's
# safety class and SID inverse kind, and whether it is one of the "dangerous
# trio" (F2/F5/F9) that share the one safe-write law (plan 3.9).
#
# Regenerate the AUTO-GENERATED taxonomy functions in
# STDLIB/iii/katabasis/cycle_family.iii via:
#     bash COMPILER/BOOT/gen_cycle_family.sh
# The build's drift gate (gen_cycle_family.sh --check) fails if cycle_family.iii's
# generated block diverges from this file (plan 6.9 / FR-9), so the cycle
# taxonomy the Gate dispatch reads can never drift from the plan-3.0 table.
#
# Each row maps to the hand-written enum constants in cycle_family.iii:
#   family const = KCF_F<id>_<name>      (e.g. KCF_F1_READ_METAL)
#   class  const = KCF_CLASS_<class>     (e.g. KCF_CLASS_READ_ONLY)
#   inv    const = KCF_INV_<inverse>     (e.g. KCF_INV_IDENTITY)
# gen_cycle_family.sh asserts every referenced constant exists; a row naming a
# constant cycle_family.iii does not define is a build-stopping error (never a
# silent undefined-symbol downstream).
#
# Fields (whitespace-delimited):  id  name  class  inverse  dangerous
#   id         u32  -- family id 1..N, ascending and contiguous.
#   name       str  -- family name; forms KCF_F<id>_<name>.
#   class      str  -- safety class; forms KCF_CLASS_<class>.
#   inverse    str  -- SID inverse kind; forms KCF_INV_<inverse>.
#   dangerous  0|1  -- 1 iff the family is in the safe-write-law trio (plan 3.9).
# Lines starting with '#' are comments. Blank lines ignored.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# id  name         class         inverse      dangerous
1     READ_METAL   READ_ONLY     IDENTITY     0
2     WRITE_METAL  WRITE_NEG     RECORDED     1
3     CENSUS       READ_ONLY     IDENTITY     0
4     SNAPSHOT     POSITIVE      COW          0
5     DESCEND      DESCEND_NEG   VMEXIT       1
6     OBSERVE      OBSERVE       IDENTITY     0
7     SELF_VERIFY  READ_ONLY     IDENTITY     0
8     CAP_OP       GOVERNANCE    CAP          0
9     COPROC       WRITE_NEG     GPU          1
